criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Breast cancer diagnostic at I and II stages;

          -  Similar adjuvant chemotherapy;

          -  More than 18 years.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Current smoking

          -  Diabetic neuropathy;

          -  Hypertension uncontrolled;

          -  Heart failure;

          -  Clinical depression;

          -  Skeletal muscle impairment which not allow physical exercise.
